{
  "stem": "27340.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And incidentally, I've recently just been invited to join the alumni group, so that's rather nice.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] I had to start all over again, yes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But this is why the Dean remembered me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] He said we'd be delighted to have you back, but you've got to start at the rock bottom again, which I was prepared to do.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I took qualification in mechanical engineering.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But always having been very interested in human beings and-- and-- and-- and human contacts, I then took an additional qualification in production or industrial engineering, as it's known in America, or process engineering, which gives you far more contact with human beings.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And ultimately, through various jobs that I selected myself-- I stayed in a job no more than two years because in those days, jobs were easy to be obtained, especially in engineering, it gave me a chance always to advance rather than wait until, in fact, the vacancy occurred.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And ultimately, I became chief production engineer in an organization, and then was asked-- no, then I applied for a job with an American company of management consultants.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I got a job with them, and I worked for a short time in Sweden, and in the United States, and Canada, and then I was asked to go to Germany.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I returned to England.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I returned to England, and I completed my studies here in England.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, the homeland.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, well, I don't look upon it like that, but I did return to Germany, yes, yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I consider it to be a foreign country [INAUDIBLE] as any others.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I discussed that to some extent with my wife, and that's really-- I was married then, and we had--",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had our first child on the way.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
